        <section class="welcome-note" id="welcome">
                
<div class="container">
    <div class="header-part"><h2 class="section-title">Welcome to Ferrum</h2><p style="text-align: center;">At the foot of the Northern Drakensberg, the Ferrum Falcon has made a remarkable school it&#8217;s home. Through Ferrum to the future! At Ferrum we do things differently, we do it better.</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">The Ferrum Falcons do it with excellence!</p>


<p></p>
